WEBVTT

00:00:06.639 --> 00:00:08.279
Your balance is almost depleted.

00:00:08.919 --> 00:00:10.599
Your next payment is due on the 12th.

00:00:11.519 --> 00:00:12.599
Call me when the drip is done.

00:00:19.399 --> 00:00:20.600
The patient is on an IV right now.

00:00:20.679 --> 00:00:21.960
If you have questions, ask them quickly.

00:00:27.399 --> 00:00:28.039
Sorry to bother you.

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:30.039
We brought you some fruit.

00:00:31.079 --> 00:00:31.760
Have a seat.

00:00:39.359 --> 00:00:41.119
We'll just ask a few questions and go.

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:43.960
Do you know if your brother A Xin

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:45.560
ever delivered medical supplies

00:00:46.119 --> 00:00:47.479
for this nursing home?

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.119
Has your brother Xin Qili

00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:03.880
been using some other means

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.200
to pay for your medical bills?

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:08.760
We aren't asking this without proof.

00:01:09.480 --> 00:01:10.760
We checked your medication records,

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:12.000
and your payment details.

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:14.359
They don't match your actual condition

00:01:14.359 --> 00:01:15.560
or your health status at all.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.799
And this nursing home

00:01:18.439 --> 00:01:19.760
is giving you unauthorized drugs.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.120
And they're not cheap.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:24.159
Based on the leads we have,

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.519
your brother Xin Qili

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:27.959
is suspected of illegal transactions.

00:01:28.519 --> 00:01:29.480
About all of this,

00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:30.920
do you know anything?

00:01:35.519 --> 00:01:36.560
My brother...

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:52.480
My brother

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:54.920
has been doing some shady things.

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.319
Because of my illness,

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:58.959
he really had no other choice.

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.599
People like us,

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:02.879
with no money,

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.040
no connections,

00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:07.079
we can only wait to die when we get sick.

00:02:08.199 --> 00:02:08.919
I know that money

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:10.599
definitely wasn't earned legally.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:13.120
But I want to live.

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:15.159
I want to stay alive.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:16.840
Is that against the law?

00:02:18.919 --> 00:02:20.599
He never told me

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:21.919
what he was doing,

00:02:22.439 --> 00:02:23.800
or where the money came from.

00:02:24.319 --> 00:02:25.360
And I never asked.

00:02:27.639 --> 00:02:29.319
Because I was afraid if I asked,

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:30.719
I wouldn't be able

00:02:30.719 --> 00:02:32.560
to live with myself anymore.

00:02:36.360 --> 00:02:37.080
Are you done asking?

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.439
The patient needs to rest now.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.520
Let's stop here for today.

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.280
If you remember anything new,

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:46.439
let us know anytime.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.360
Officer Zhang.

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:55.120
Chen Yongjiang is dead.

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:56.599
What about his company?

00:02:57.919 --> 00:02:59.479
The second shareholder took it over.

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:00.879
What is it?

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.400
After all, he killed my brother.

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:14.960
Did your brother ever tell you anything

00:03:15.039 --> 00:03:16.479
about the Fengmao Company?

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:18.520
Is that so?

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:20.479
Zhang Heng.

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:27.280
Excuse me.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.400
It really is you.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:36.840
What case are you working on?

00:03:36.919 --> 00:03:38.159
I keep running into you here lately.

00:03:41.199 --> 00:03:42.560
How's Paopao doing these days?

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:44.039
Thanks to you, brother-in-law.

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.400
Since you're back at the law firm,

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:48.360
the hospital bills are more manageable.

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.360
That's great.

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.000
Same as before,

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:54.759
let me know anytime if you need anything.

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:00.360
Come home for dinner when you have time.

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:11.960
Did you hear?

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.000
That girl next door,

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.439
her brother died.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.199
She's the only one left in her family.

00:04:17.319 --> 00:04:18.120
Poor thing.

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:20.439
The past couple of days,

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:21.720
people have been keeping watch downstairs.

00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:24.319
I bet she owes someone money.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:27.160
Where do you hear this stuff all day?

00:04:27.399 --> 00:04:28.959
She's got a caregiver here every day.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:30.160
That doesn't come cheap.

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:37.959
Come in.

00:04:38.839 --> 00:04:40.079
Sorry to bother you.

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:42.560
I'm a family member from the next room.

00:04:43.839 --> 00:04:44.680
My family said

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:46.000
you're staying here all by yourself.

00:04:46.079 --> 00:04:47.360
These are freshly made.

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:48.959
Eat them while they're hot. Don't be shy.

00:04:55.639 --> 00:04:56.839
Those people outside,

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:58.639
what's really going on?

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.319
Those people outside...

00:05:04.319 --> 00:05:05.040
Luo Xiao.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.519
You think you're an exception?

00:05:11.639 --> 00:05:13.519
Do... do we know each other?

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:26.279
You didn't just take Brother Mao's place,

00:05:27.519 --> 00:05:29.199
you took on his risks too, didn't you?

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:33.240
What are you trying to say?

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.639
I'm guessing you've already met Ruan Chen.

00:05:37.639 --> 00:05:38.720
Those people outside,

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.600
he sent them to watch me.

00:05:41.519 --> 00:05:44.240
Because of the evidence A Xin left me.

00:05:45.279 --> 00:05:48.639
A Xin paid for this life of mine.

00:05:49.879 --> 00:05:51.480
So I have to stay alive.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.040
You have to help me.

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.399
Because I can help you too.

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:07.000
Otherwise, look at those men outside.

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:09.120
When are they coming tomorrow?

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:10.120
I don't know.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:14.079
Whether they're coming for me,

00:06:14.759 --> 00:06:15.680
or coming for you,

00:06:15.879 --> 00:06:17.360
or going after your daughter,

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.839
I have no idea.

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:20.959
You don't believe me?

00:06:23.079 --> 00:06:23.959
Then what about Zhang Heng?

00:06:25.079 --> 00:06:26.199
Do you even know?

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:27.800
He's already found out

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:29.879
that the nursing home's bills are shady.

00:06:30.399 --> 00:06:32.480
He found out my medical records are fake.

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:35.920
If he keeps digging like this,

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:38.600
how sure are you you'll get out clean?

00:06:39.879 --> 00:06:40.800
What do you mean?

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:48.079
I'm getting blisters on my lips.

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:50.519
These transactions are way too scattered.

00:06:50.839 --> 00:06:52.040
It's just like Yi Zhan.

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:53.279
They're all straw-man accounts.

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:54.800
After bouncing around a few times,

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:56.000
it goes back to Fengmao.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.639
It's all stuff we already know.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:06.879
Besides this,

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:10.319
Fengmao runs many businesses,

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:13.120
but Ruientai Pharma shows up a lot.

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:15.560
It's also in the nursing home's books.

00:07:17.319 --> 00:07:18.879
Ruientai Pharma repeatedly

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:20.399
wired money to Fengmao.

00:07:20.639 --> 00:07:21.920
Each transfer was hundreds of thousands.

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:24.839
All marked "project promotion payments."

00:07:28.879 --> 00:07:29.600
Look.

00:07:30.519 --> 00:07:31.199
Just as I thought.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.639
No project approval process.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:38.079
No reconciliation documents.

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:39.879
I just checked too.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:42.720
Zero project partnership with Fengmao.

00:07:43.439 --> 00:07:45.160
Ruientai isn't a shell company,

00:07:45.439 --> 00:07:47.279
but it has fake projects with Fengmao.

00:07:48.439 --> 00:07:50.439
The nursing home's books are dirty.

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:52.680
Xin Youna's medical records were faked.

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:54.360
This Xin Qili

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:57.519
is the middleman for the bank and Fengmao.

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:00.439
Then what links Ruientai and Fengmao?

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:04.120
Looks like you don't know yet.

00:08:05.079 --> 00:08:06.600
Could you be a bit clearer?

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:12.839
This nursing home

00:08:13.439 --> 00:08:14.800
can treat your daughter's illness,

00:08:15.279 --> 00:08:17.120
but it requires some illegal drugs.

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:19.560
Banned substances.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.920
Foreign drugs.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.759
Looks like you just moved in recently.

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.800
The director hasn't consulted you yet.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:29.920
Otherwise, why would you think

00:08:29.959 --> 00:08:31.959
a county-level nursing home like this

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.840
could grow to such a scale,

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.480
with patients coming from out of town

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.559
in an endless stream every day?

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:44.320
This nursing home

00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:46.399
has an underground drug supply chain.

00:08:46.759 --> 00:08:49.080
A Xin convinced Brother Mao

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.440
to add this to the laundering pipeline.

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:53.399
They put the money in,

00:08:53.799 --> 00:08:55.200
under the guise of buying drugs,

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:56.840
clean it, then move it out.

00:08:57.919 --> 00:08:59.080
Of course, part of that money

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:00.679
was to buy medicine for me.

00:09:01.279 --> 00:09:04.279
Then Brother Mao saw profits dropping.

00:09:04.559 --> 00:09:05.559
He wanted to shut it down.

00:09:06.159 --> 00:09:07.120
A Xin refused.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:10.559
That's why the "accident" happened.

00:09:12.039 --> 00:09:14.799
So you mean this nursing home

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:17.080
is also a downstream link for Ruan Chen.

00:09:18.039 --> 00:09:19.519
It's not just this nursing home.

00:09:20.399 --> 00:09:24.240
Pharma company, Ruan Chen, Brother Mao,

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:27.320
they each have their own interests.

00:09:27.919 --> 00:09:29.600
They cooperate, but they also clash.

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:32.360
A Xin just sweet-talked Brother Mao

00:09:32.759 --> 00:09:34.960
into running the money through here.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:39.240
Zhang Heng has dug this far.

00:09:39.919 --> 00:09:41.039
That means he already has

00:09:41.039 --> 00:09:42.440
evidence of Fengmao's money laundering.

00:09:42.679 --> 00:09:44.000
He's also tracked down A Xin.

00:09:44.639 --> 00:09:46.759
He might have caught Ruan Chen's tail.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.200
If that's the case,

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:54.320
why not give the evidence to the cops?

00:09:54.919 --> 00:09:57.440
If the police go after the bank next,

00:09:58.320 --> 00:09:59.320
by working with me,

00:10:00.639 --> 00:10:02.039
what would you gain?

00:10:03.639 --> 00:10:05.240
I'm not after any benefit.

00:10:08.279 --> 00:10:10.399
I want to stay alive.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.799
Zhang Heng can't give me that.

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.320
The drugs, yes.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:22.600
I can give you leverage on the bank,

00:10:23.679 --> 00:10:25.519
but you have to guarantee my safety

00:10:25.759 --> 00:10:26.840
and the drug supply.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:32.279
Your leverage,

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.120
how much weight does it carry?

00:10:38.159 --> 00:10:39.720
Only two hundred moved this week.

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:42.600
A Xin's side collected as planned.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:45.519
Keep the reserve at one hundred.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:47.559
Check the books one more time.

00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:49.440
The heat is on lately.

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:51.399
The cash flow

00:10:51.960 --> 00:10:53.679
must strictly follow the chain.

00:10:57.399 --> 00:10:59.120
I need some time to think about it.

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:03.799
Those guys outside are just scaring you.

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:05.279
There are cameras everywhere here.

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:06.600
They wouldn't dare touch you.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:08.080
If there's any issue, call security,

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:09.799
or call me anytime.

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:11.639
I'll leave you to it.

00:11:16.879 --> 00:11:18.799
The first transfer was exactly three days

00:11:18.799 --> 00:11:20.440
before Xin Youna checked in.

00:11:21.919 --> 00:11:23.120
The last transfer

00:11:23.240 --> 00:11:25.240
was a week before A Xin died.

00:11:25.919 --> 00:11:27.360
The timing's too much of a coincidence.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:30.320
Excluding the Ruientai payments,

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:33.000
Fengmao's other accounts ran normally.

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:35.120
No external promotional projects,

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:37.120
no obvious funding gaps either.

00:11:37.759 --> 00:11:38.960
In other words,

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:40.840
the transactions between the two of them

00:11:41.159 --> 00:11:42.879
weren't for actual goods,

00:11:43.159 --> 00:11:44.279
nor were they money laundering.

00:11:44.919 --> 00:11:46.679
But they're strongly tied to the nursing home

00:11:46.679 --> 00:11:47.759
and to that brother and sister.

00:11:48.519 --> 00:11:49.679
We've got our breakthrough.

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:51.720
These past two years,

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.879
we must find a way to shut Fengmao down.

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:54.759
Otherwise,

00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:55.720
it's too dangerous.

00:11:56.799 --> 00:11:57.559
Alright.

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:01.279
Lawyer Luo.

00:12:02.039 --> 00:12:03.080
After you, Mr. Ruan.

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:24.120
A Xin's sister,

00:12:24.919 --> 00:12:26.919
Xin Youna has something important.

00:12:27.799 --> 00:12:28.440
You go

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:30.000
and get it for me.

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:33.279
What is it?

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:36.600
What is it?

00:12:37.759 --> 00:12:39.080
It can't be dumplings, can it?

00:12:40.799 --> 00:12:42.120
I'm not trying to put you in a tough spot,

00:12:42.679 --> 00:12:43.720
but you need to realize

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:46.480
who you're in the same boat with now.

00:12:49.159 --> 00:12:50.320
Do you have any idea?

00:12:50.679 --> 00:12:52.120
What she's holding

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.480
is a ticking time bomb.

00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:56.559
Once it goes off,

00:12:57.679 --> 00:12:58.919
not only you, Luo Xiao,

00:12:59.519 --> 00:13:00.799
or me, Ruan Chen,

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:04.440
the whole chain behind us gets exposed.

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:08.080
You only see the money,

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:11.679
if you knew where it came from,

00:13:12.399 --> 00:13:13.720
whose hands it passed through,

00:13:14.559 --> 00:13:15.919
and where it ended up,

00:13:17.559 --> 00:13:20.000
you'd be at her room right this second.

00:13:20.559 --> 00:13:21.879
Do whatever it takes,

00:13:22.279 --> 00:13:23.440
and bring that thing to me.

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:28.960
I'm not capable of that.

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:34.200
Your guys can only stake out outside,

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:35.360
let alone me.

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:37.600
Zhang Heng has already contacted her.

00:13:38.159 --> 00:13:39.000
At the slightest move,

00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:40.360
she'll call the cops immediately.

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:48.039
I won't let you do this for nothing.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.600
Money laundering is one thing,

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:52.679
getting that item is another.

00:13:53.240 --> 00:13:54.279
They're two different matters.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.159
The guy your wife cheated with,

00:14:03.039 --> 00:14:03.879
you know him, right?

00:14:06.480 --> 00:14:07.440
Just say the word,

00:14:08.039 --> 00:14:09.440
and he disappears, just like that.

00:14:16.080 --> 00:14:17.480
I can help you get the item,

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:20.360
but hold off on Feng Zhan for now.

00:14:22.399 --> 00:14:23.320
He's still useful to me.